    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226870/extras/2c30dcf6cad3fa9e2ef254b6113c58f6.avif?t=1749388441\" width=616 height=72 /></span>作为魔王的女儿，莉莉娜无忧无虑地活在巨大的城堡中，直到勇者前来砍了她爹。现在失去恶魔之力后，她只能悲惨地活在一个人人都厌恶她的小镇上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了改变自己的声誉和生活质量，莉莉娜接受了勇者讨伐怪物的任务，并逐渐开始适应战斗。在魔王曾经的得力助手迪亚哥的建议下，她悄悄工作以取得六个护符，这些能让她进入封印之塔，取回失去的力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226870/extras/c60db91b14588757d188f39e851681ae.avif?t=1749388441\" width=616 height=73 /></span>莉莉娜将周游世界，探索众多地下城以取得全部的六个护符。利用元素魔法属性相克击倒拦路的凶猛怪物，通过特殊的渠道可以获得新的技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226870/extras/607623be3dffdbe4d0c28c78c6d00bf6.avif?t=1749388441\" width=616 height=73 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226870/extras/3218d8734ab9b81b274f8f8cec3a3019.avif?t=1749388441\" width=616 height=274 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226870/extras/5e4daef1b3b6c5b6f0a3b991227d91e2.avif?t=1749388441\" width=616 height=274 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226870/extras/308071a667e4217c9dec8675e5b5cdae.avif?t=1749388441\" width=616 height=274 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226870/extras/24a7e53272b087a7fc4eeff503477c60.avif?t=1749388441\" width=616 height=274 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226870/extras/6677b1bcc02f4447e7d2b3c2787cce0f.avif?t=1749388441\" width=616 height=274 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3226870/extras/325cbf786f6297d10ea70d7d7199088b.avif?t=1749388441\" width=616 height=73 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装备可通过战斗习得新的技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >怪物都有自己的元素弱点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >怪物图鉴会展示每个怪物的细节。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个迷宫都有独特的专属首领怪。</p>",
